  "text": "Although the theoretical Superluminal waves encountered in this paper cannot be exactly produced, due to their infinite energy, they can be approximated with a finite aperture radiator and retain the essential characteristics (limited diffraction and Superluminal group velocity) over a large depth of field [CITATION_1] . Each component (wavelet)",
